Need for Speed: The Run is competing throughout America.
Review
A journey, in principle neglected, is complicated due to a series of unfair neglect of a routine journey during the turn of tomorrow.
In a certain extent it was achieved to cover expectations, but this does not serve anything, if, in reality, it was not intended to do anything extraordinary.
The new release, to which the title is added to The Run, awakened great expectations before its premiere.
He promised it would give new aires to the old Need for Speed racing saga and, as shown, appears as a game that shouldn’t end up being again a genre of action without more.
We also feel curious to know how the inserted scenes would be left, where the main character descends from the car and walks by his own foot.
As it usually happens in the NFS series, the results don’t vary much compared to what we expected.
There are races that can be given as acceptable, but in the total computing points are lost due to absurd failures, which have already appeared in the series for years.
In reality, errors cannot be called, but it’s rather the incomprehensible failure of the programmers.
The adventure begins very well.
You are introduced into a story, whose protagonist, Jack, has certain personal problems; to solve them, you are offered to participate in an illegal race throughout America.
You sit on the wheel on the west coast, in San Francisco, and your mission is to get the first to New York.
The idea is to offer something interesting.
The route is divided into ten stages and then more than fifty races.
It follows that each race takes place on a different route and the stages are localized in different environments, which are quite diverse and interesting.
In this way, one does not even remotely have the feeling that the game always offers the same thing.
Some of the environments are even pleasant to see, although the technical level of the graph is equivalent to the previous delivery of the series.
It is nothing of the other world.
But walking through the desert, the autumn landscape or the high snow-covered mountains produce a very pleasant visual effect.
Moreover, races are diversified from time to time by an atypical element.
So, for example, in the desert you find a sand storm that decreases visibility.
Instead, in the mountains you have to be careful not to be buried by an avalanche.
According to this, each of the races is well developed.
There are only a few models, but that is enough.
For a moment, you try to advance a number of rivals required (the normal in a classic race), then you try to win time (chronometrated classic duel) and then you are waiting for a duel against a single opponent.
In the midst of all this sometimes appears the police, which does not only make things even more difficult.
The novelty is the landscapes outside the car.
Interactive animations are presented when Jack, in most cases, has to escape someone and you have to help him, always pressing the right button at the right time.
Nothing complicated.
It is surprising, however, that there are a lot less landscapes in the game than you could expect (in particular there are only three).
But the final result is positive, because this element does not get to be annoying and, in the already mentioned context, it is one of the elements that make the game more interesting.
The driving model follows the footprints of the previous episodes.
That means that today it is no longer a great thing, but it cannot be said to be bad.
If you are looking for a realistic simulation, you can now look elsewhere.
But a fairly action-conceived race is quite suitable for this style of driving, although we will be able to find something better among the competition games.
So far, everything in order.
But the problems arise after a certain time.
Unlike the correct driving models, the same thing is no longer happening with collisions.
From games of this type you can’t expect to recre deformations and complicated collisions, but in fact before a blow against any object, you can’t predict how your car will react, with which not everything is in order.
It is typical that, by making a very adjusted advance or circulating the car with a normal traffic, there are only light rocks, but in other almost identical situations, your car ends up making uncontrolled piruetes.
Or it ends completely destroyed.
Thanks to the reset system, there are no big problems, but it can put you in bad mood.
The resetings are scheduled in such a way that, when you suffer an accident or you leave the track, the game returns you to the last rescue point on the track.
However, in each race there are only five resets available.
If you consume them all, you have to restart the race from the beginning.
So it’s nothing more than a help in case something goes wrong, but it’s not very reliable.
Sometimes, neither reset helps, it only helps to learn the given stage of memory.
A great disadvantage of the game is that the same facts are repeated in different places.
In some curves, for example, you have to enter in a specific way; otherwise, they are impossible to take.
Other times you find somewhere "civil" vehicles always with the same configuration, even if you are the first, fifth or arrive five minutes before or after.
This makes you crazy especially in situations, when you see that two cars that go to the meeting in opposite directions, your contrincant advances without problems, but when you arrive, you have to turn or freeze.
It’s the same when you arrive, because it’s scheduled because the “surprise” will always happen in front of your nose.
The opponents also have another advantage.
During the whole game you will get to sites where, without taking into account the moment, you will always advance the same opponent on the same site.
In addition, this happens at the end of the game, on a long bridge, which is even more shocking.
Your opponent must come before you, at any price.
When it goes in front of you, it makes it difficult for you to see the cars that come in front, so at the beginning you can make the car papilla.
You can understand the idea of creating a game with maximum doses of suspense and adrenaline, but the execution is so apparent that it will surely disappoint you immediately.
And it’s a pity, because although the model of the journey is simple, the game is fun and with action, so it’s often not possible to follow in detail what’s happening or where.
And it really doesn’t matter if the merit takes the idea with fifty exclusive tracks or the ranking in the race so that you don’t get bored, or anything else.
An unusual idea is the change of cars during the races.
You have to be attentive to the gas pipes next to the road, because just there you have to change the car, although in the vast majority of cases you will be enough what you have.
The cars are divided into three categories.
Sports are suitable for urban areas, strong American cars for straight highways and exotic super sports for technical driving, for example, by mountain roads with curves.
In addition to the main narrative thread also appears a thread of parallel challenges, that is, there are races in concrete places that you will know by the stories.
Here you will get not only medals, but also experience points for your profile, which serves both for challenges and stories.
At the top level, the driver opens several possibilities, starting with the car and ending with funds for the profile.
At the same time, an online Autolog feature is connected, which compares your results with those of other players and provides other community features.
One of the most difficult elements to understand is how the last career in history is made.
With the car you get to the tunnel of the metro (pass), where you get to run in the dark through the roads (pass).
The speed meter marks you between 150 and 200 km/h (pass) and, suddenly, the metro convoy reaches you behind and takes you in front without more.
In the writing we will surely have a discussion about this for several days, about whether during the programming of the game no one thought even a little or if the authors really take us for a panda of bubbles.
The technical part of the game is nothing extraordinary, but at least the general visual effects result in most of the cases pleasant, sometimes even superb.
What a sadness that, in the most tensive moments, the image quality is reduced and, sometimes, in a serious way.
This affects primarily the accidents where there are many participants involved, when the continuous image quality is no longer valid.
The audio is good and the soundtrack is a matter of tastes.
In order to be pleasant to most of the youth group, the soundtrack belongs to the category "every one of his father and mother", but it can be assumed that no one would buy the game only for his music.
The final sensation of Need for Speed: The Run is quite confusing.
If the game avoided absolutely foolish errors, we would have trouble saying that The Run is the best NFS game of the last few years.
It gives the feeling that the game is not finished.
The fun is secured, but prepare because the mistakes will hit you in the eyes with the strength of an airport reflector.
The coros of the University of Carolina will participate in the concert "Students of Third-First".
The joint celebration of International Student Day and the anniversary of the Third-First Revolution as a musical experience will take place for the third time at the Festa Academica festival.
At the same time, 20 corals of secondary and university centers will be presented.
The festival will turn around two concerts on November 17.
“The University of Carolina has a high participation in the festival.”
Among the current chorus are the coral of the Faculty of Pedagogy and the Faculty of Humanities, in the committee of the festival is the rector Václav Hampl,” said the organization’s chief, Jakub Čaloun.
The entire festival summit is the free entrance for all the public to the concert of the secondary courses, which will be held on March 17 at 14 hours in front of the National Technical Library in Dejvice.
The program includes the participation of the Czech jazzist Karel Růžička and his Celebration Jazz Mass.
The night will be held in the places of celebration of the Municipal House in Vynohrady the concert "Students of Third-First", in which university corals will participate, including the Chorus of the Carolina Uninversity.
The Academic Festa aims not only to honor the International Student Day and to remember the 22nd anniversary of the Third-First Revolution, but also to present the public the coral music at the highest level and to favour collaborative creation among young people.
The main organizer is the Czech Union of Corals in collaboration with the Jan Kepler Secondary Institute.
All the events were supported by the mayor of Prague, Bohuslav Svoboda, and the rector of the University of Carolina, Václav Hampl.
The festival will take place between 16 and 20 November between Prague and Pardubice.
The calendar offers, in addition to celebrative concerts, a whole series of musical events, improvised student shows and morning concerts.
The interested will be able to find more information on the festival page www.festaacademica.cz
