In 2000 he moved to the capital of the Valley and, after performing the corresponding courses, specialized in lofoscopy, which is the study of the friction skin, i.e. the palms of the hands and feet.
The week of the operative against alias Alfonso Cano to Eliazar warned him to wear clothes for a minimum of three days.
