For a dactiloscopist of Sijín de Cali the recognition that President Juan Manuel Santos made to Eliazar González, in the press round by the operative against "Cano", is very significant.
Many people don’t know our work.
Dactyloscopy is an accurate, error-free science that can become key in the resolution of crimes.
Apart from the identification of bodies, lofoscopists support investigations for crimes such as theft and murder and confirm the identity of the people captured.
When they are captured, many criminals present false cards or do not have papers.
We take the fingerprint and look for them in the database.
